data.text: And it's a movie where they wear trenchcoats, these black trenchcoats. This group of students went to a school and they started killing people. And they promoted in the press that it was because of the movies that these kids were into and the games that they played. And they pretty much went into the school and they did everything like a shoot-them-up game, like a game, like Halo, or these games where this first person shoots and you go through the level and you have to destroy the enemies and promote to the next level.
